  "texts": [
    "We need to act ethically and be adaptable to ensure we remain ethical as new information arises.",
    "Our goal with these 10 rules is not to provide a whole new workflow to switch to but rather to combine much of the \"best practices wisdom\" into one workflow that also acknowledges the human component of both the work and the impact of data-intensive research.",
    "Computational Biology | https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pcbi.1012232July 18, 2024"
